Package com.intellij.ide.navigationToolbar

Interface NavBarModelExtension

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNavBarModelExtension, DefaultNavBarExtension, GrNavBarModelExtension, ScratchFileServiceImpl.NavBarExtension, ServiceViewNavBarExtension

    public interface NavBarModelExtension
    The interface has a default implementation (DefaultNavBarExtension) which is normally registered as last. That means that custom implementations are called before the default one - with the exception of adjustElement(PsiElement) method, for which the order is reverse.
